SAN DIEGO COUNTY DIGEST: CAMP PENDLETON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
One Marine was killed and another was injured early Tuesday morning when the 
speeding car in which they were riding slammed into a parked car in San 
Clemente, police said. 
</P>
<P>
