<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art; Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA083089-0038 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 100993 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 30, 1989, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 1; Column 5; Sports Desk 
