POSSESSIONS; MOLDAVIA (USSR); ETHNIC GROUPS; GOVERNMENT REFORM; USSR -- 
GOVERNMENT; COMMUNIST PARTY (USSR); LANGUAGE; DEMONSTRATIONS -- USSR; STRIKES 
</P>
